source.name: Defense Logistics Agency Press Release Compendium
source.description: This dataset is a compendium of Defense Logistics Agency (DLA) Public Affairs Press Releases from 1997 to the present.  The collection can be accessed by year and is regularly updated to disseminate DLA news and information to the public.   Sign up to receive Press Releases and News Articles from DLA Public Affairs.
